# Rule 8: Suspicious Scheduled Task Creation
# --------------------------------------------------
# Description: Detects the creation of a new scheduled task that points to 
# suspicious directories like \Windows\Temp or \Users\Public, a common persistence method.
# 
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1053.005 (Scheduled Task/Job: Scheduled Task)
# Severity: Medium
# 
# Logic (Sigma-style):
#   - EventID: 4698 (A scheduled task was created)
#   - Command contains: ('\Temp\', '\Public\', 'powershell.exe', 'cmd.exe')
#   - Action: Register / Create
# 
# Log Source: Windows Security Log (Object Access: Task Scheduler)
